# ─── EmailJS — Investor Brochure Email Delivery ──────────────────────────────
#
# Setup steps:
#   1. Create a free account at https://www.emailjs.com/
#   2. Add an Email Service (Gmail / Outlook / SMTP) → copy the Service ID
#   3. Create Template 1 (investor autoresponder):
#      - Sends to: {{to_email}}
#      - Subject: "Your DRIV Investor Brochure"
#      - Body: include PDF brochure as attachment or a download link
#      - Variables: from_name, from_email, phone, invest_range, city, message
#   4. Create Template 2 (team notification):
#      - Sends to your team email
#      - Subject: "New Investor Interest — {{invest_range}}"
#      - Variables: same as above
#   5. Get your Public Key from Account → API Keys
#   6. Copy this file to .env and fill in the values below
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

VITE_EJS_SERVICE_ID=service_xxxxxxx
VITE_EJS_TEMPLATE_ID=template_xxxxxxx
VITE_EJS_NOTIFY_ID=template_xxxxxxx
VITE_EJS_PUBLIC_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
